                            </msItem>      
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <locus from="77va" to="79rb"/>
                            <title>List of Patriarchs of Alexandria</title>
                            <note>The last named in No. 109 - 
                                <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11721PeterVIIAlex"><roleName type="title">ʾAbba</roleName> Ṗeṭros</persName>.
                                Cf. <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/3JX2BR53"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1912Patriarches"/><title level="a">Liste des patriarches d'Alexandrie, d'après le ms. éth. no. 3 de M. E. Delorme</title><title level="j">Revue de l'Orient Chrétien</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Sylvain</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Grébaut</t:surname></author><date>1912</date><biblScope unit="volume">2ième série, Tome VII (XVII), No. 2</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">212-216</biblScope><note type="accessed">2025-03-05</note><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/revuedelorientch171912pari/page/212/mode/2up</note></bibl>.</note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <locus from="79va" to="84va"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1994Mazgab">Mazgaba hāymānot</title>
                            <note>The end is missing. The text ended before the end of the account of the third Council 
                                (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ ጉባኤ፡ ሣልስ፡ </foreign>).</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዘኢይሰደቅ፡ ዋሕድ፡ ዘኢይትነፈቅ፡ መሐሪ፡ ርሑቀ፡ መዓት፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ንጽሕፍ፡ ዘንተ፡ 
                                መጽሐፈ፡ ዘይሰመይ፡ መዝገበ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ከመ፡ ይለብውዎ፡ ማኅበረ፡ መሃይምናን፡ ወመሃይምንት፡ ካህናት፡ 
                                ወዲያ<sic resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ቶ</sic>ናት፡ አዕሩግ፡ ወሕፃናት፡ </incipit>
                        </msItem>
